                "imgDesc": "<p>Smaller flames split from the Stadium of the Sacred Flame, intended for the Turnfire Night ritual conducted by the Scions of the Canopy. They contain a blessed power that dispels the darkness.<br><span style=\"color: #FFE14B\">Interact with lit braziers</span> to obtain the Sacred Flame's protection. Then <span style=\"color: #FFE14B\">collect and throw Flamegranates</span> to cause explosions that will scatter the Abyss's power.</p>",
